content.text: Review this Crafting page at 325px width (small phone). This page has category filters and a data table of craftable items. Check for: 1. Layout overflow - anything extending past viewport? 2. Touch targets - filter chips/buttons/links at least 44px? 3. Text readability - font sizes adequate? 4. Filter usability at narrow width 5. Table usability 6. Any visual bugs. Be specific about any issues, include CSS selectors if possible.
